Patrons...

14
00:00:54,740 --> 00:00:57,670
I'd like to close 
the restaurant soon.

15
00:00:57,670 --> 00:00:59,390
We're alive here, now....

16
00:00:59,390 --> 00:01:01,180
Listen, sir...

17
00:01:01,180 --> 00:01:02,830
...and we don't 
need to go anywhere.

18
00:01:03,180 --> 00:01:04,740
Isn't that enough for you?

19
00:01:04,740 --> 00:01:06,980
Hey, are you listening to me?!

20
00:01:10,020 --> 00:01:11,440
Shut up.

21
00:01:12,970 --> 00:01:15,190
Can I eat him? Can I eat him?

22
00:01:15,190 --> 00:01:17,090
Today, it's my treat.

23
00:01:17,630 --> 00:01:18,920
Take your time.

24
