Now that I think about it,

25
00:01:28,170 --> 00:01:30,500
I've wondered about this before.

26
00:01:31,020 --> 00:01:33,880
Where did I come from, and where am I going?

27
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:44,120
Stay with me! 
Stay with me, Jimmy!

28
00:01:45,030 --> 00:01:47,330
Excuse me! 
Please let me through!

29
00:01:47,950 --> 00:01:50,050
Please, let me 
take a look at him.

30
00:02:07,330 --> 00:02:09,100
He'll be all right now.

31
00:02:10,260 --> 00:02:11,730
Thank you so much!

32
